    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[<p class="HELM_exercise">Exercise <br></p>
<p>Transpose the formula {@eqn@} for {@b1@}</p>
<p>[[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]]</p>]]></text>
		</questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[<p>Since we are trying to make {@b1@} the subject of the formula we first, to both sides of the equation, {@addsub@} \({@coef1*b1@}\) which gives: \[{@eqn1@}\] We then subtract 17 from both sides of the equation giving: \[{@eqn2@}\]. Finally we divide both sides of the equation by {@coef2@} giving: \[{@ta1@}\]</p>]]></text>
		</generalfeedback>
